Hello! My name is Sarah, and I’m with RT 6 Boozers, where we offer a great selection of drinks and a lively atmosphere. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I'm looking to know more about your happy hour specials.

Absolutely! I can help with that. May I first have your name, please?

Sure, my name is John.

Thank you, John! Now, could you provide me with your email address so I can send you the details?

Of course, it’s john.doe@example.com.

Great! And can you also let me know your phone number, please, including your area code?

Sure, it’s area code one two three, four five six, seven eight nine zero.

Thank you, John! We appreciate your information. Our happy hour is from four PM to seven PM, and you can enjoy discounts on all drinks.

That sounds fantastic! I’ll definitely check it out.

Thank you for your time, John! If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
